# 17 - Debate Simulator (Multi-Agent with Profiles)
# Simulate a debate using fast models for rapid back-and-forth

NAME debate
INPUT topic
INPUT rounds DEFAULT 3

AGENT pro FROM agents/optimist.md REQUIRES "fast"
AGENT con FROM agents/devils-advocate.md REQUIRES "fast"

GOAL opening "Present the debate topic: $topic. Frame the key question and stakes."
GOAL argue "Present arguments for and against $topic." USING pro, con
GOAL rebut "Respond to opposing arguments with counterpoints." USING pro, con
GOAL conclude "Summarize both sides and identify the strongest arguments and key tensions."

LOOP debate_rounds USING argue, rebut WITHIN $rounds
RUN wrap_up USING conclude
